                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_7251">كتاب الضرادى</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Persian treatise on the conjugation of Arabic verbs by Fakhr al-Dīn Zarrādī (here spelt Z̤arrādī) Dihlavī (active 1253-1337 or 1347)</p>
                        <p>Copious annotations in margins</p>
                        <p>Calligraphic naskh</p>
                        <p>Not dated</p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per" otherLangs="ara">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                  </msItem>
