                        <persName xml:lang="per" key="person_f5618" type="supplied">ظهير بن محمود بن مسعود العلوي</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_2690">Zubdat fī ʿilm al-ṣarf</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_2690">زبدۃ في علم الصرف</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Treatise on Arabic grammar: laws of permutation or inflection applying to irregular or weak verbs</p>
